  - key: levelselect.level.suburban_02.name
    vietnamese: "Ch\xE1y B\u1EBFp"
    english: Kitchen Fire
  - key: levelselect.level.suburban_02.description
    vietnamese: "Ng\u01B0\u1EDDi g\u1ECDi b\xE1o c\xF3 ch\xE1y b\u1EBFp trong m\u1ED9t c\u0103n nh\xE0 \u1EDF khu d\xE2n c\u01B0. H\xE3y thu th\u1EADp th\xF4ng tin \u0111i\u1EC1u ph\u1ED1i v\xE0 \u1ED5n \u0111\u1ECBnh cu\u1ED9c g\u1ECDi."
    english: Caller reports a kitchen fire in a suburban house. Collect the dispatch details and stabilize the call.
  - key: levelselect.level.suburban_02.objective
    vietnamese: "Ho\xE0n th\xE0nh giai \u0111o\u1EA1n cu\u1ED9c g\u1ECDi v\xE0 chu\u1EA9n b\u1ECB b\xE1o c\xE1o s\u1EF1 c\u1ED1 \u0111\u1EC3 \u0111i\u1EC1u ph\u1ED1i."
    english: Complete the call phase and prepare the incident report for dispatch.
  - key: levelselect.level.suburban_02.difficulty
    vietnamese: "Th\u01B0\u1EDDng"
    english: Normal
  - key: levelselect.level.suburban_03.name
    vietnamese: "Ch\xE1y Ph\xF2ng Gi\u1EB7t"
    english: Laundry Room Fire
  - key: levelselect.level.suburban_03.description
    vietnamese: "Ch\xE1y ph\xF2ng gi\u1EB7t c\xF3 c\u1EA3 nguy c\u01A1 v\u1EC1 gas l\u1EABn \u0111i\u1EC7n. H\xE3y thu th\u1EADp \u0111\u1EA7y \u0111\u1EE7 b\xE1o c\xE1o v\xE0 \u0111\xE1nh gi\xE1 m\u1EE9c \u0111\u1ED9 nghi\xEAm tr\u1ECDng c\u1EE7a s\u1EF1 c\u1ED1."
    english: Laundry room fire with both gas and electrical hazards present. Collect the full report and assess the incident severity.
  - key: levelselect.level.suburban_03.objective
    vietnamese: "Ho\xE0n th\xE0nh giai \u0111o\u1EA1n cu\u1ED9c g\u1ECDi v\xE0 chu\u1EA9n b\u1ECB b\xE1o c\xE1o s\u1EF1 c\u1ED1 \u0111\u1EC3 \u0111i\u1EC1u ph\u1ED1i."
